title: The Dark Maze v1.06 [PD]
description:
When April decided to enter the maze, Vince sighed and reluctantly, came after her. Soon, what seemed like a simple task, began to take an unexpected turn.
Go with Vince in his search through the maze and discover the truth that lies inside.

Play through 10 levels of increasing difficulty, unlock a play mode with unlimited random mazes and get ready to new story mode levels and new play modes that will be added with free updates.
Discover the story with in-game and cinematic sequences at the beginning and end of each episode. Enjoy hand-drawn graphics and immersive instrumental music.

---------------------------------

It is recommended a medium/high resolution.
It is recommended a 1GHz processor or higher.
